[b]Auth Vulnerability:[/b] There is no way to verify customer sessions or authorize purchases.
[b]Payment Block:[/b] Customers are stuck at their carts because the system can't communicate with external banks.
[b]Fulfillment Gap:[/b] There is no way to dispatch events to the warehouse once an order is placed.
[/ul]"
